<h2><img src="/media/13049117/ski-chalet-big.jpeg" alt="ChaletHero" data-udi="umb://media/266dcff8df4943ca8ca745c6bb1662c2" /></h2>
<h2>Inghams catered ski chalets</h2>
<p>Our catered ski chalets are the perfect base for your alpine holiday.</p>
<p>Cosy with warm and welcoming furnishings and décor, our ski chalets feature all the comforts of home. Full of thoughtful touches, each chalet boasts an inviting atmosphere and plenty of space to relax after a day on the slopes.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ffe21dfd7ad849c3bd332fa3a4124dad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ffe21dfd7ad849c3bd332fa3a4124dad}" class="c-btn">Ski chalet deals</a></p>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Our Chalet service</h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13107234/service-800x400.jpg" alt="ChaletService&amp;Hosts" data-udi="umb://media/e6e7b6783e954928aadcb3cb80243361" /></p>
<p><strong>Chalet hosts</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Our Chalet Hosts are destination experts</li>
<li>Our hosts will be on hand to offer breakfast, afternoon tea and dinner 6 days of the week.</li>
<li>They also maintain the cleanliness of the communal areas.</li>
<li>Most of our Chalet Hosts are avid skiers and snowboarders so can share their knowledge of the slopes and resorts.</li>
<li>We use eco-friendly cleaning products throughout our properties and we have stopped using single use plastic.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Chalet catering</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>We have designed our menu and products to help improve our carbon footprint.</li>
<li>Breakfast is included on every morning of your holiday and consists of a continental buffet or 6 morning a week, a hot serve option.</li>
<li>Afternoon tea with a variety of cakes will be available 6 days of the week</li>
<li>Dinner will be served 6 nights of your chalet holiday, consisting of a 4-course choice dinner, starting off with prosecco apéritif.</li>
<li>During dinner, there is a choice of 3 reds, 3 whites and 1 rosé wine, variety of beer and soft drinks.</li>
<li>If you have any dietary requirements, you will need to let our reservations team know at time of booking.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Ski chalets in Europe</h2>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a href="#italy" data-anchor="#italy">Italy</a> | <a href="#austria" data-anchor="#austria">Austria</a> | <a href="#france" data-anchor="#france">France</a></h3>
<p>Here are some Inghams hand-picked chalets taken from our wide selection across European resorts. Chalets tailored for you - from large group sized, quietly located or lift-side. Take your pick and find the chalet to host your perfect ski holiday. </p>
<h3>Ski chalets in Austria</h3>
<p>Austria is a popular skiing destination due to its vast ski areas - offering high-quality chalets.</p>
<div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div id="austria" class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cb76241406db44c7b6930c63fc375ad3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb76241406db44c7b6930c63fc375ad3}" title="Chalet Fauner A">Chalet Fauner A</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>St Anton</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Sleeps 16, 8 bedrooms</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13103264/inghams-fauner-st-anton-dining-living-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletFaunerA" data-udi="umb://media/49ebe2eaf00a4e10b46d6b54a618c6df" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Ideal for groups looking to enjoy everything the Arlberg ski area has to offer, in a quiet, well decorated chalet, just 5 minutes’ walk to the town centre.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/5418da4fce4d4595b128c12f64372bc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5418da4fce4d4595b128c12f64372bc9}" title="Chalet Albona (Mountain Lodge)">Chalet Albona</a></h3>
<p><strong>St Anton</strong></p>
<p>Sleeps 10, 5 bedrooms</p>
<p><img src="/media/13103255/chalet-albona-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletAlbona" data-udi="umb://media/3f6bc67ffab742c1949993387953f2e8" /></p>
<p>The Mountain Lodge chalet selection, is situated in the popular Gastig area of St. Anton, consists of four modern chalets all sharing a stylish building.</p>
</div>
