<h2 style="text-align: left;">Ski chalets in France</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">France is forever a favourite skiing destination, there is plenty of skiing to be had. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div id="france" class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85}" title="Chalet La Rocheure">Chalet La Rocheure</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Val d'Isere</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Sleeps 12-13, 6 bedrooms</p>
<p><img src="/media/13103260/chalet-la-rocheure-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletRocheure" data-udi="umb://media/a57acbc1df28465caca1b25b6e0598b3" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">This stunning chalet is modern, spacious and charmingly decorated with Alpine antiques. It sleeps 14-15, with all bedrooms having access to en-suite facilities.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85}" title="Chalet La Rocheure"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/1de1d81241e3469f8b30346a82c00993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1de1d81241e3469f8b30346a82c00993}" title="Chalet L'Ancolie">Chalet L'Ancolie</a></h3>
<p><strong>Méribel</strong></p>
<p>Sleeps 10-11, 5 bedrooms</p>
<p><img src="/media/13103261/chalet-lancolie-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletAncolie" data-udi="umb://media/341b6c4f657944918b186771aaf0b7e7" /></p>
<p>This superb chalet was built in traditional Savoyard style, in a quiet location and set back and slightly above the main road, offering good mountain views.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
