<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/40ee75dda3d24f7fa43e5f94dcd3cad1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/40ee75dda3d24f7fa43e5f94dcd3cad1}" title="Chalet Arktic">Chalet Arktic</a></h3>
<p><strong>Tignes</strong></p>
<p>Sleeps 14, 7 bedrooms</p>
<img src="/media/13107232/chalet-arktic-dining-area-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletArktic" data-udi="umb://media/c8adc49e0b8b46cbafbd2e403b438c78" /><br />
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This popular chalet offers seven bedrooms, furnished to a high standard with en-suites. Sip your morning coffee from the sun terrace with spectacular views. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925" href="/{localLink:umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925}" title="Chalet Mathilde">Chalet Mathilde</a></h3>
<p><strong>Val Thorens</strong></p>
<p>Sleeps 8, 4 bedrooms</p>
<img src="/media/13103262/chalet-mathilde-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletMathilde" data-udi="umb://media/643abc80088c4a6c8510c0db0e0b9f02" />
<p>The spacious chalet features a sun terrace, sauna,  steam room and cosy lounge area with log burning stove. <span>You can ski or walk 100 metres to the piste.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div><br /><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8}" title="Chalet Marie">Chalet Marie</a></h3>
<p><strong>Avoriaz</strong></p>
<p>Sleeps 14, 7 bedrooms</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8}" title="Chalet Marie"><img src="/media/13107233/chalet-marie-500x250.jpg" alt="ChaletMarie" data-udi="umb://media/feb6775cb2014804be61b35a931cdcb8" /></a></p>
<p>A modern, spacious and charmingly decorated chalet with Alpine antiques. It sleeps 14-15, all bedrooms with en-suite facilities.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f086bd745df54ae9944d84f9e210cec5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f086bd745df54ae9944d84f9e210cec5}" title="Chalet Secret de Neige">Chalet Secret de Neige</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Alpe d'Huez</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Sleeps 12-14, 6 bedrooms</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13098028/chalet-secret-de-neige-500x250.jpg" alt="chaletsecret" data-udi="umb://media/73a64e1e997d4394a55de6903984a889" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">With its fantastic location it's hard to beat, not to mention the modern interiors and wooden architecture that reflects its traditional French alpine roots.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div><br /><br />
<div style="text-align: center;"><br /><br />
